data.description: Get a list of valid categories.
data.name: Categories
category_id
data.description: IDs of the category to restrict the search to.  Multiple category ids should be separated by commas.

data.name: deal_rating
data.description: Restrict search to certain deal ratings

data.name: end_date
data.description: Only include events up to this date and time

data.name: max_results
data.description: Maximum number of results to return.  Default is 200

data.name: metro_region_id
data.description: IDs of the metro regions to restrict the search to.  Multiple metro region IDs should be separated by commas.

data.name: performer_id
data.description: IDs of the performers to restrict the search to (home games only)

data.name: query
data.description: Free form text for a general search (event, city, venue, performer, etc)

data.name: secondary_performer_id
data.description: IDs of the performers to restrict the search to (away games only)

data.name: start_date
data.description: Only include events after this date and time
